First version of the Mediastation client on Android (tested on a HTC Desire running Froyo (Android 2.2)).
Mediastation is a PC media server that can stream your media (audio, video and photo) to any UPnP device (PS3 for instance). You can also access your media from a web interface (full Ajax) and now on any Android smartphone!
